Market Segmentation: 
The brushless DC motor market is segmented on the basis of type, speed, end-user, stator winding and voltage. The growth among segments helps you analyse niche pockets of growth and strategies to approach the market and determine your core application areas and the difference in your target markets.
On the basis of type, the brushless DC motor market is segmented into inner rotor brushless DC motors and outer rotor brushless DC motors.
Based on speed, the brushless DC motor market is segmented into <500 RPM, 501–2000 RPM, 2001–10000 RPM and >10000 RPM.
Based on end-user, the brushless DC motor market is segmented into manufacturing, medical devices, automotive, consumer electronics, HVAC equipment, aerospace & defense  and others.
Based on stator winding, the brushless DC motor market is segmented into single phase, two phases and three phases.
The brushless DC motor market is also segmented on the basis of voltage into 0-750 Watts, 750 watts to 3 kW, 3 kW to 75 kW and above 75 kW.
